<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>The method Code\Reflection\DocBlockReflection::reflect() extracts the clean DocComment, but does not use it for the DocBlockScanner.
Not only, that it would simplify the DocBlockScanner, it even fails sometimes to extract Tags from the DocBlock.</p>

<p>I would suggest to replace the line 265 with the following:</p>

<p>$scanner = new DocBlockScanner($this-&gt;cleanDocComment);</p>

